column5: I think black women are even more marginalized,  coming from a black woman. Anyways all we can do is try to survive and make a life worth living for ourselves.
As a 24f who's upset about having no friends I can understand this. It doesnt get better.
I'm a black Muslim 24f I'm about to message you
May I ask you how you threw it out for good?
So in your opinion is it worse or better
I've seeked help half my life
